# ğŸ Bronco Shop

## Overview

Bronco Shop is a simple fullâ€‘stack web application that simulates an online university bookstore. Users can browse products, create a profile, add items to a cart, and complete a checkout process. The project was built to demonstrate core web development concepts using **Node.js**, **Express**, and basic frontâ€‘end technologies.

This project was developed as part of a class assignment and focuses on functionality, routing, and serverâ€‘side handling of user input.

---

## Features

* Browse bookstore items with images and prices
* Shopping cart functionality
* Checkout page in a separate tab
* Payment method input form
* Server logs all user actions and form inputs in the VS Code terminal

---

## Technologies Used

* **Node.js**
* **Express.js**
* **EJS** (Embedded JavaScript templates)
* **HTML / CSS / JavaScript**
* **Multer** (for image uploads)

